data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home, featuring an updated kitchen, and a finished basement. The first floor features a large living and dining room with sliding doors that lead to the patio and fenced-in backyard.  The kitchen has ample updated cabinets, and countertops, as well as a built-in microwave, dishwasher, and a large pantry for storage. The cozy powder room rounds out the first floor.  The second floor features 3 large bedrooms and a full bathroom. The finished basement is perfect for gatherings. It features a large living space, bar, laundry room, and a separate office/workout room. This home is located in the heart of the Cleveland Metroparks which includes biking/walking trails and a nature center. Home Warranty Included!
